00:38:44,364 --> 00:38:46,301
- He's still in it.
- I think he's still in it.

837
00:38:46,325 --> 00:38:47,409
Yeah, no, he...

838
00:38:47,534 --> 00:38:50,204
But there was more of him than...
He was an awesome dog.

839
00:38:50,287 --> 00:38:53,099
- No one told Chuck he was cut.
