00:39:10,140 --> 00:39:11,451
And this was all improvised a lot.

846
00:39:11,475 --> 00:39:15,604
All the playing around. They told them
to have fun, and they were able to do it.

847
00:39:16,146 --> 00:39:19,083
That pink bike that she rides right
there is the one that we actually had

848
00:39:19,107 --> 00:39:20,793
- on the side of the road.
- At the gas station?

849
00:39:20,817 --> 00:39:22,528
So, she had a chance to practice.

850
00:39:22,611 --> 00:39:25,364
Yeah, and I said,
"Make sure we have it in the mall".

851
00:39:25,447 --> 00:39:27,533
So we brought it in. It was great.

852
00:39:28,283 --> 00:39:29,618
<i>Watership Down</i> book.

