877
00:40:51,450 --> 00:40:53,290
It was a day shoot.
It's a night shoot...

878
00:40:53,493 --> 00:40:57,623
Well, it's supposed to be set at night,
but we shot it during the day,

879
00:40:57,706 --> 00:41:01,418
because we're dealing
with the constraints of shooting kids.

880
00:41:01,877 --> 00:41:04,117
- Oh, right.
