00:41:06,882 --> 00:41:08,717
The other kids were
all local casting, right?

883
00:41:09,968 --> 00:41:12,095
A lot of them were,
but a lot of them weren't.

884
00:41:12,179 --> 00:41:15,891
I mean, we actually lucked out with
who was available when and where.

885
00:41:16,016 --> 00:41:18,310
