- What?</i>

886
00:41:18,393 --> 00:41:19,645
<i>But only tonight.</i>

887
00:41:19,728 --> 00:41:21,448
I remember we had
to do a very quick

888
00:41:21,855 --> 00:41:23,815
wardrobe adjustment on their stuff

889
00:41:23,899 --> 00:41:26,401
- like seconds before shooting.
