00:41:47,339 --> 00:41:48,632
It's an abandoned mall.

899
00:41:48,715 --> 00:41:51,468
It's at night.
It could have been really shabby.

900
00:41:52,511 --> 00:41:56,264
But everywhere we could try
and find color, we'd put it in there.

