00:42:07,943 --> 00:42:09,653
Dystopia never look so pretty.

905
00:42:10,112 --> 00:42:12,531
<i>Look, we're not just
a bunch of dead weight.</i>

906
00:42:16,034 --> 00:42:18,704
And we didn't have a lot of time
in the mall,

907
00:42:18,829 --> 00:42:22,541
because we were also
setting up a lot of the stunt scenes

