00:44:26,206 --> 00:44:29,084
is even though he is the comedic relief,
he's also the skeptic.

948
00:44:29,876 --> 00:44:34,005
He's the one who's
the least trusting of Ruby

949
00:44:34,381 --> 00:44:36,633
when they first meet her, and, um...

