00:44:48,103 --> 00:44:51,231
But he also has that,
as an actor, such a range.

955
00:44:51,314 --> 00:44:54,568
And you can see that sensitivity
come through in moments like this.

956
00:44:56,653 --> 00:44:59,281
<i>My dad's a police detective, so...</i>

957
00:44:59,489 --> 00:45:02,284
Yeah, this scene
was fast and furious.

958
00:45:05,912 --> 00:45:07,330
But it turned out very simply.

