That voice is
Dean Zimmerman's daughter.

984
00:46:15,732 --> 00:46:17,084
- Is that right?
- Yeah.

985
00:46:20,612 --> 00:46:21,613
<i>Charles!</i>

986
00:46:21,947 --> 00:46:23,341
That's one of those things, like,

987
00:46:23,365 --> 00:46:25,405
"Who are we gonna get to do that?
Oh, let's just..."

988
00:46:28,536 --> 00:46:29,579
Super cute.

989
00:46:30,413 --> 00:46:33,166
But that moment when they smile
at each other, I just love that.

990
00:46:34,459 --> 00:46:37,337
<i>So, we're gonna
take the next exit, and...</i>

991
00:46:37,837 --> 00:46:40,382
So much of this movie
was happening in that van.

