00:49:44,816 --> 00:49:47,837
This to me is some of my favorite
stuff from Harris in the movie here.

1052
00:49:47,861 --> 00:49:50,113
- Just very delicate.
- Yeah.

1053
00:49:51,030 --> 00:49:53,241
It was one of those dangerous things
in post.

