we caught that moment."

1077
00:51:06,564 --> 00:51:10,151
- "It's so beautiful and rare."
- This is a great moment.

1078
00:51:10,235 --> 00:51:12,153
Sort of a near-kiss.
She wants connection,

1079
00:51:12,278 --> 00:51:14,739
but she's afraid of what happens
when she has it.

1080
00:51:17,408 --> 00:51:19,261
That's' why all those scenes
were in color.

