00:51:22,872 --> 00:51:26,376
'cause it was so pretty that it
was almost fairy tale pretty,

1083
00:51:26,459 --> 00:51:29,087
so we had to de-prettify it
just a hair in color.

1084
00:51:29,170 --> 00:51:30,170
Yeah.

