1179
00:56:03,861 --> 00:56:04,946
Yes, he did.

1180
00:56:06,739 --> 00:56:07,823
<i>Blaze of glory.</i>

1181
00:56:07,907 --> 00:56:09,033
And this van.

1182
00:56:09,116 --> 00:56:11,136
Since this is the last time
we're gonna be seeing it,

1183
00:56:11,160 --> 00:56:12,995
it was just nice just to see it

1184
00:56:13,120 --> 00:56:14,681
in the sort of
idyllic beautiful resting place.

1185
00:56:14,705 --> 00:56:16,825
- It's a character in the movie.
