1186
00:56:17,625 --> 00:56:19,811
We spent a lot of time trying
to figure out what song to play here.

1187
00:56:19,835 --> 00:56:21,939
This is one of the better
song cues of the movie, I think, too.

1188
00:56:21,963 --> 00:56:23,965
- This is a great one.
- Yeah.

1189
00:56:24,799 --> 00:56:26,527
I think, Dan, this is
what you listen to

