00:56:27,593 --> 00:56:29,512
Yep. That's where we got it from.

1192
00:56:31,013 --> 00:56:32,223
The old Pilates mix.

1193
00:56:35,434 --> 00:56:36,954
And this was great.
I remember just...

1194
00:56:36,978 --> 00:56:40,565
We kind of randomly picked up shots,
and this was where Kramer, our DP,

1195
00:56:40,690 --> 00:56:42,567
was hanging off the back of a golf cart.

1196
00:56:42,692 --> 00:56:46,195
- Trying to get a golden hour...
- Yeah, as the sun was going down.

1197
00:56:46,320 --> 00:56:47,881
- Yeah.
- And then we also had

1198
00:56:47,905 --> 00:56:51,409
some drone shots going here,
